<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>플라슈티컬즈 | 재생의료를 임상으로 연결합니다</title>
  <meta name="description" content="태반 유래 줄기세포 및 엑소좀 기반 재생의료 기술로 임상 진입 개발 전략을 설계합니다. Backward Design 방법론 기반 첨단재생의료 컨설팅 전문기업.">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link rel="stylesheet" as="style" crossorigin href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/orioncactus/pretendard@v1.3.9/dist/web/variable/pretendardvariable-dynamic-subset.min.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="tokens.css">
  <style>
    /* ══════════════════════════════════
       HERO
    ══════════════════════════════════ */
    #hero {
      min-height: 100vh;
      background: linear-gradient(155deg, #050e1c 0%, #071525 40%, #0d1e34 100%);
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      position: relative; overflow: hidden;
      padding: calc(var(--nav-h) + 56px) 32px 80px;
    }
    #hero::before {
      content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0;
      background:
        radial-gradient(ellipse at 20% 55%, rgba(0,121,250,.18) 0%, transparent 55%),
        radial-gradient(ellipse at 82% 30%, rgba(109,171,255,.10) 0%, transparent 50%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    #hero::after {
      content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0;
      background-image:
        linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,.025) 1px, transparent 1px),
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,.025) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 64px 64px;
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .hero-content {
      position: relative; z-index: 1;
      max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center;
    }
    .hero-badges {
      display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 8px; flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }
    .hero-badge {
      font: 600 11px/1 var(--mono); color: var(--accent2);
      padding: 6px 14px;
      background: rgba(109,171,255,.10);
      border: 1px solid rgba(109,171,255,.22);
      border-radius: 20px; letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }
    .hero-h1 {
      font-size: clamp(38px, 5.5vw, 68px); font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 1.14; letter-spacing: -0.04em;
      color: var(--white); margin-bottom: 14px;
    }
    .hero-h1 span {
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #6dabff, #a8dcff);
      -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
    }
    .hero-en {
      font: 400 14px/1 var(--mono); color: rgba(255,255,255,.32);
      letter-spacing: 0.5px; margin-bottom: 32px;
    }
    .hero-desc {
      font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.8; color: rgba(255,255,255,.52);
      max-width: 520px; margin: 0 auto 48px;
    }
    .hero-btns { display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .hero-scroll {
      position: absolute; bottom: 36px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
      display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
      font: 500 10px/1 var(--mono); color: rgba(255,255,255,.22);
      letter-spacing: 2.5px; z-index: 1;
      animation: hero-scroll-bounce 2.4s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    .hero-scroll svg { width: 20px; height: 20px; }
    @keyframes hero-scroll-bounce {
      0%, 100% { opacity: 0.4; transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0); }
      50% { opacity: 0.7; transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(9px); }
    }

    /* ══════════════════════════════════
       WHAT WE DO — 3 Pillars
    ══════════════════════════════════ */
    .pillar-grid {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 24px;
      margin-top: 52px;
    }
    .pillar-card {
      background: var(--white); border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 40px 32px;
      text-align: center;
      transition: box-shadow .3s var(--ease), border-color .3s, transform .3s var(--ease);
    }
    .pillar-card:hover {
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
      border-color: rgba(0,121,250,.2);
      transform: translateY(-6px);
    }
    .pillar-icon {
      width: 64px; height: 64px; background: var(--accent-light);
      border-radius: 18px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      margin: 0 auto 24px; transition: background .3s;
    }
    .pillar-card:hover .pillar-icon { background: var(--accent); }
    .pillar-icon svg { width: 28px; height: 28px; color: var(--accent); transition: color .3s; }
    .pillar-card:hover .pillar-icon svg { color: var(--white); }
    .pillar-num {
      font: 700 11px/1 var(--mono); color: var(--accent);
      letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .pillar-title {
      font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text);
      margin-bottom: 6px; letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    }
    .pillar-en {
      font: 500 12px/1.3 var(--mono); color: var(--text3); margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .pillar-desc { font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--text2); }

    /* ══════════════════════════════════
       CORE MESSAGE — Backward Design
    ══════════════════════════════════ */
    .backward-wrap {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 64px; align-items: start;
    }
    .backward-quote {
      font-size: clamp(20px, 2.4vw, 28px); font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 1.38; letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .backward-en {
      font: 400 13px/1.4 var(--mono); color: var(--text3); margin-bottom: 36px;
    }
    .backward-points { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; }
    .backward-point {
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px;
      padding: 16px 20px; background: var(--white); border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 12px; transition: border-color .2s, box-shadow .2s;
    }
    .backward-point:hover { border-color: rgba(0,121,250,.2); box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm); }
    .backward-point-num {
      font: 700 12px/1 var(--mono); color: var(--accent);
      background: var(--accent-light); min-width: 32px; height: 32px;
      border-radius: 8px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .backward-point-text {
      font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text); line-height: 1.4;
    }
    .flow-wrap {
      background: var(--white); border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 36px 40px;
    }
    .flow-label {
      font: 600 11px/1 var(--mono); color: var(--text3);
      text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 2px; margin-bottom: 28px;
    }
    .flow-step {
      display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 16px;
      padding: 16px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .flow-step:last-child { border-bottom: none; padding-bottom: 0; }
    .flow-step-num {
      width: 36px; height: 36px; background: var(--accent);
      border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font: 700 12px/1 var(--mono); color: var(--white); flex-shrink: 0;
      margin-top: 2px;
    }
    .flow-step:last-child .flow-step-num { background: var(--navy); }
    .flow-step-name { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 3px; }
    .flow-step-en { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text3); font-family: var(--mono); }

    /* ══════════════════════════════════
       CONSULTING SERVICES
    ══════════════════════════════════ */
    .consulting-grid {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 24px;
    }
    .c-process {
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
      padding: 28px 32px; background: var(--white); border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius); margin-top: 40px;
      overflow-x: auto; flex-wrap: nowrap;
    }
    .c-step { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; flex-shrink: 0; }
    .c-step-box {
      background: var(--accent-light); border: 1px solid rgba(0,121,250,.15);
      border-radius: 10px; padding: 12px 20px; text-align: center; min-width: 92px;
    }
    .c-step-box.final { background: var(--navy); border-color: var(--navy); }
    .c-step-num {
      font: 600 10px/1 var(--mono); color: var(--accent);
      letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 6px;
    }
    .c-step-box.final .c-step-num { color: rgba(255,255,255,.5); }
    .c-step-name { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text); }
    .c-step-box.final .c-step-name { color: var(--white); }
    .c-arrow svg { width: 18px; height: 18px; color: var(--accent2); }

    /* ══════════════════════════════════
       RESEARCH PLATFORM
    ══════════════════════════════════ */
    .research-banner {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #071525 0%, #0e2040 100%);
      border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 52px 48px;
      position: relative; overflow: hidden; margin-bottom: 48px;
    }
    .research-banner::before {
      content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0;
      background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 70% 50%, rgba(0,121,250,.18) 0%, transparent 55%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .research-banner-inner { position: relative; z-index: 1; }
    .rb-overline {
      font: 600 11px/1 var(--mono); color: var(--accent2);
      letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .rb-title {
      font-size: clamp(24px, 3vw, 36px); font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--white); letter-spacing: -0.035em; margin-bottom: 8px; line-height: 1.25;
    }
    .rb-en { font: 400 13px/1 var(--mono); color: rgba(255,255,255,.38); }
    .app-grid {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 20px;
    }
    .app-card {
      background: var(--white); border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 36px 28px; text-align: center;
      transition: box-shadow .3s, border-color .3s, transform .3s;
    }
    .app-card:hover { box-shadow: var(--shadow-md); border-color: rgba(0,121,250,.2); transform: translateY(-5px); }
    .app-icon { font-size: 40px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .app-title { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 8px; letter-spacing: -0.025em; }
    .app-desc { font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.65; color: var(--text2); }

    /* ══════════════════════════════════
       PLATFORM — R&BD
    ══════════════════════════════════ */
    .dev-flow {
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 8px; padding: 36px 40px;
      background: var(--white); border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius); margin: 40px 0 48px;
      overflow-x: auto; flex-wrap: nowrap;
    }
    .dev-step { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 10px; flex: 1; min-width: 80px; text-align: center; }
    .dev-circle {
      width: 60px; height: 60px; background: var(--accent-light);
      border: 2px solid rgba(0,121,250,.15); border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font: 600 11px/1.3 var(--mono); color: var(--accent);
      text-align: center; transition: all .3s;
    }
    .dev-step:hover .dev-circle { background: var(--accent); color: var(--white); border-color: var(--accent); }
    .dev-circle.target { background: var(--navy); color: var(--white); border-color: var(--navy); }
    .dev-name { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text); line-height: 1.3; }
    .dev-arrow { color: var(--accent2); flex-shrink: 0; }
    .dev-arrow svg { width: 20px; height: 20px; }

    /* ══════════════════════════════════
       ABOUT
    ══════════════════════════════════ */
    .about-grid {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 56px; align-items: start;
    }
    .about-mission-card {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #071525 0%, #0e2040 100%);
      border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 40px;
      position: relative; overflow: hidden; margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .about-mission-card::before {
      content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0;
      background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 80% 20%, rgba(0,121,250,.2) 0%, transparent 55%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .mission-inner { position: relative; z-index: 1; }
    .mission-overline {
      font: 600 11px/1 var(--mono); color: var(--accent2);
      letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 20px; display: block;
    }
    .mission-quote {
      font-size: clamp(16px, 1.8vw, 20px); font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.55;
      color: var(--white); letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      border-left: 3px solid var(--accent); padding-left: 20px;
    }
    .org-chart {
      background: var(--gray-bg2); border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 36px;
    }
    .org-chart-label {
      font: 600 11px/1 var(--mono); color: var(--text3);
      letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 28px;
    }
    .org-tree { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 0; }
    .org-row { display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 12px; }
    .org-node {
      background: var(--white); border: 1.5px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 10px; padding: 10px 20px;
      font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text);
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }
    .org-node.ceo { background: var(--navy); color: var(--white); border-color: var(--navy); }
    .org-node.cto { background: var(--accent-light); color: var(--accent); border-color: rgba(0,121,250,.2); }
    .org-line {
      width: 2px; height: 22px; background: var(--border); margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .org-h-connector {
      display: flex; justify-content: center; position: relative; margin-bottom: 0;
    }
    .org-h-connector::before {
      content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0;
      left: calc(50% - 52px); right: calc(50% - 52px);
      height: 2px; background: var(--border);
    }
    .org-h-connector .org-vline {
      width: 2px; height: 22px; background: var(--border);
    }
    .org-desc {
      margin-top: 24px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--text2);
    }

    /* ══════════════════════════════════
       RESPONSIVE
    ══════════════════════════════════ */
    @media (max-width: 960px) {
      .pillar-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 16px; }
      .backward-wrap { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; }
      .consulting-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
      .app-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 32px; }
    }
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      #hero { padding: calc(var(--nav-h) + 32px) 20px 60px; }
      .pillar-card { padding: 32px 24px; }
      .consulting-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .c-process { padding: 20px; }
      .research-banner { padding: 36px 28px; }
      .dev-flow { padding: 24px; }
      .app-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }
    @media (max-width: 540px) {
      .hero-h1 { font-size: clamp(32px, 9vw, 44px); }
      .backward-wrap { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗ -->
<!-- ║  NAV                                                     ║ -->
<!-- ╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝ -->
<nav id="plt-nav" class="on-hero">
  <div class="nav-inner">
    <a href="index.html" class="nav-logo">
      <div class="nav-logo-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-1 17.93c-3.95-.49-7-3.85-7-7.93 0-.62.08-1.21.21-1.79L9 15v1c0 1.1.9 2 2 2v1.93zm6.9-2.54c-.26-.81-1-1.39-1.9-1.39h-1v-3c0-.55-.45-1-1-1H8v-2h2c.55 0 1-.45 1-1V7h2c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2v-.41c2.93 1.19 5 4.06 5 7.41 0 2.08-.8 3.97-2.1 5.39z" fill="white"/></svg>
      </div>
      Placeuticals
    </a>

    <ul class="nav-menu">
      <li class="nav-item">
        <button class="nav-link" type="button">
          서비스
          <svg viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none"><path d="M2 4l4 4 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="nav-drop">
          <a href="#consulting">개발 전략 컨설팅</a>
          <a href="#research">연구 플랫폼</a>
          <a href="#platform">통합 R&amp;BD 플랫폼</a>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="nav-item">
        <button class="nav-link" type="button">
          회사소개
          <svg viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none"><path d="M2 4l4 4 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="nav-drop">
          <a href="#about">회사소개</a>
          <a href="about.html#location">오시는길</a>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="nav-item">
        <button class="nav-link" type="button">
          고객지원
          <svg viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none"><path d="M2 4l4 4 4-4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="nav-drop">
          <a href="support.html#qna">Q&amp;A</a>
          <a href="#contact">Contact Us</a>
        </div>
      </li>
    </ul>

    <a href="#contact" class="nav-cta">문의하기</a>

    <button class="nav-ham" id="nav-ham-btn" type="button" aria-label="메뉴 열기">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
        <path d="M4 6h16M4 12h16M4 18h16" stroke-linecap="round"/>
      </svg>
    </button>
  </div>

  <!-- Mobile Drawer -->
  <div class="nav-drawer" id="nav-drawer">
    <div class="nav-drawer-section">
      <div class="nav-drawer-label">서비스</div>
      <a href="#consulting">개발 전략 컨설팅</a>
      <a href="#research">연구 플랫폼</a>
      <a href="#platform">통합 R&amp;BD 플랫폼</a>
    </div>
    <div class="nav-drawer-section">
      <div class="nav-drawer-label">회사소개</div>
      <a href="#about">회사소개</a>
      <a href="about.html#location">오시는길</a>
    </div>
    <div class="nav-drawer-section">
      <div class="nav-drawer-label">고객지원</div>
      <a href="support.html#qna">Q&amp;A</a>
      <a href="#contact">Contact Us</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</nav>


<!-- ╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗ -->
<!-- ║  S1 · HERO                                               ║ -->
<!-- ╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝ -->
<section id="hero">
  <div class="hero-content">
    <div class="hero-badges">
      <span class="hero-badge">REGENERATIVE MEDICINE</span>
      <span class="hero-badge">TRANSLATIONAL STRATEGY</span>
      <span class="hero-badge">인증 벤처기업</span>
    </div>
    <h1 class="hero-h1">재생의료를 <span>임상으로</span><br>연결하는 개발 전략</h1>
    <p class="hero-en">Translating Regenerative Science into Clinical Strategy</p>
    <p class="hero-desc">
      태반 유래 줄기세포 및 엑소좀 기반 연구와<br>
      임상 진입 및 개발 전략(Translational Development Strategy)을 수행합니다.
    </p>
    <div class="hero-btns">
      <a href="#consulting" class="btn-primary">서비스 보기 →</a>
      <a href="#contact" class="btn-ghost">문의하기</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-scroll" aria-hidden="true">
    SCROLL
    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
      <path d="M12 5v14M5 12l7 7 7-7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
    </svg>
  </div>
</section>


<!-- ╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗ -->
<!-- ║  S2 · WHAT WE DO                                         ║ -->
<!-- ╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝ -->
<section id="what-we-do" class="section">
  <div class="inner">
    <div class="section-label">What We Do</div>
    <h2 class="section-h2">세 가지 역량으로 <span>임상 진입</span>을 설계합니다</h2>
    <p class="section-sub">기초연구부터 임상까지, Backward Design을 기반으로 전주기 개발 전략을 수행합니다.</p>

    <div class="pillar-grid">
      <!-- 01 연구 -->
      <div class="pillar-card">
        <div class="pillar-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
